Trinity::

She was tired and yawned, showing her sabertooth fangs. She rubber 
her eyes with her paws and was soon asleep.  

She dreamed of her parents and some of the happy memories she had of 
them.  She dreamed, the she was still with her mother back on the 
ship. She was playing tag with her mother, being chased around the 
halls of the ship.

She giggled in her sleep.
